{
  "page": "Chatana Qo",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Princess</span><br />Chatana Qo<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Arrow of Jhahar</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Arrow of Jhahar</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nPrincess of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Qo\" title=\"House Qo\">House Qo</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Chatana Qo</b>, the Arrow of <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jhahar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jhahar (page does not exist)\">Jhahar</a>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior_women\" title=\"Warrior women\">warrior woman</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a> and the daughter and successor of <a href=\"/index.php/Xanda_Qo\" title=\"Xanda Qo\">Xanda Qo</a>, Princess of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chatana_Qo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Chatana fought in a series of wars, which came to be known as the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Slavers%27_Wars&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Slavers&#39; Wars (page does not exist)\">Slavers' Wars</a>. The unity of the Summer Isles, that her mother achieved, did not survive Chatana's reign however, for she wed unwisely and did not rule as well as she fought.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chatana_Qo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Summer Isles.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403145231\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.101 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.394 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 433/1000000\nPreprocessor generat